tyle=3D"margin:0;margin-bottom:0px;">There=E2=80=99s an off-color term for =
these senescent legislators: the Pinewood Box Caucus, the implication being=
 that the only way they=E2=80=99ll leave the Capitol is in a coffin. Alas, =
in Congress, seniority is often a function of, well=E2=80=A6 <em>seniority<=
/em>. Members in their eighth or ninth decade of life may risk overstaying =
their welcome, but it=E2=80=99s only after many terms of service that they =
finally gain real clout=E2=80=94ascending to wildly powerful committee posi=
