yaWdodGVzdCstK1NVQlNDUklCRVJTKyUyODEyJTJGMzAlMkYyNCUyOVx1MDAyNnV0bV9jb250ZW=
50PVRoZStCZXN0KyUyNitUaGUrQnJpZ2h0ZXN0Ky0rU1VCU0NSSUJFUlMrJTI4MTIlMkYyOSUyR=
jI0JTI5XHUwMDI2dXRtX21lZGl1bT1lbWFpbF9hY3Rpb25cdTAwMjZ1dG1fc291cmNlPWN1c3Rv=
bWVyLmlvXHUwMDI2dXRtX3Rlcm09ZjZjNjA2MTdkYTQyYWJkMTJhIiwiaW50ZXJuYWwiOiJmNmM=
2MDYxN2RhNDJhYmQxMmEiLCJsaW5rX2lkIjoyMDMwNjg0fQ/2e863f1df9fabeffc1b76d1f64b=
ff029f2c217cd15a968fbf8d3177fbb62effb" style=3D"text-decoration:underline;c=
olor:#d40000;">law</a> dictates that a House vacancy is filled via special =
election, not appointment. If Granger started to decline in September and s=
ubsequently resigned, her seat would likely have remained vacant through Ja=
nuary 3, leaving her constituents without an advocate with executive branch=
 agencies, helping to secure Social
Security checks, veterans benefits, passports, etcetera. Especially with <s=
trong>Elon Musk</strong> threatening to kill the F-35 fighter jet program=
=E2=80=94a major economic concern in Fort Worth=E2=80=94the district is arg=
uably better off with a well-staffed, absent representative, than with no r=
epresentative at all.=C2=A0</p></div>
